# translating business to coding structure

Problem at hand- campaign performance

--> Business question: how to ensure that the pricing benchmarks are competitive against comptetition brands
--> Input data: we would need the spends of competition brands, which is next to impossible to guess. this would require modelling of its own
--> Output: expected output is a rating structure which needs to tell whether our pricing is equal to cheaper or expensive than competition
--> Action: this data will help leadership negotiate deals at a consolidated level to ensure our pricing stays competitive in market
